data.text:
I kinda goofed on a previous post about Misia’s album Just Ballade. Turns out the first single was Aitakute Ima. (I’ve corrected that post). Now this second single is actually Hoshi No Youni. How do I know this? It’s the chorus of the song. Doh!

Anyway, this is another great ballad and the video is even cooler because it actually features Ultraman. And I love the monsters just hanging out in a school classroom. WTF?
